{"id":618921,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/【立此存照】南充阆中网警拘留一侮辱阅兵式官兵/","date":"2019-10-01T21:45:44Z","modified":"2019-10-01T22:15:15Z","title":"【立此存照】南充阆中网警拘留一&#8221;侮辱阅兵式官兵&#8221;网民","content":"<p id=\"activity-name\" class=\"rich_media_title\">来源：<span id=\"profileBt\" class=\"rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname\">南充网警</span></p>\n<p class=\"rich_media_title\">2019年9月29日，在全国人民普天同庆喜迎新中国成立70周年之际，南充网警接网民举报，南充网民“24K纯帅”涉嫌在网上肆意发布侮辱参加70周年大庆阅兵式官兵的言论，引发广大网民的强烈愤慨。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-618922\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/6-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/6-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/6-576x1024.jpg 576w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/6.jpg 690w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-618923 size-medium\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/1-300x270.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"270\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/1-300x270.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/1.jpg 555w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-618924\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/2-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"327\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/2-276x300.jpg 276w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/2.jpg 519w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-618925\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/3-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/3-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/3-576x1024.jpg 576w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/3.jpg 690w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-618926\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/4-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/4-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/4-576x1024.jpg 576w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/4.jpg 690w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-618927\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/5-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"464\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/5-194x300.jpg 194w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/5.jpg 546w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></p>\n<p class=\"rich_media_title\">南充网警根据网民举报线索迅速开展核实工作并指令阆中网警查处。现查明：9月29日上午，网民“24K纯帅”（真实姓名，戚某龙，24岁，男，阆中人）在网上发布“精日”言论并针对国庆阅兵式多次发表不当言论，虽经其他网民提醒，仍然肆意侮辱参加阅兵式人员。阆中网警将戚某龙传唤到案后，该戚对自己的违法行为供认不讳。根据中华人民共和国《治安管理处罚法》第二十六条之规定，9月30日凌晨，阆中市公安局依法对其作出行政拘留7日的决定。目前，拘留正在执行。</p>\n<div id=\"js_content\" class=\"rich_media_content \" style=\"text-align: center\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section data-bgopacity=\"50%\" data-bglessp=\"280\" data-bgless=\"spin\" data-autoskip=\"1\">\n<blockquote>\n<section><strong>南充网警提醒：</strong>网络非法外之地，网民在网络上的言行要恪守真实客观，注重网上道德,遵守国家的有关法律法规,承担因自己的行为而引起的法律责任，逞一时口快，换来的将是法律的严惩。 </section>\n</blockquote>\n</section>\n<blockquote>\n<section><strong>CDS档案 | <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E9%98%85%E5%85%B5\">阅兵</a></strong></section>\n</blockquote>\n</section>\n</section>\n</div>\n<section></section>\n<section><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-618932\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/signal-2019-10-01-230516-150x150.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/signal-2019-10-01-230516-169x300.jpeg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/signal-2019-10-01-230516-577x1024.jpeg 577w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/signal-2019-10-01-230516.jpeg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></section>\n","author":1061,"categories":[18271,38912,38920],"tags":[39003,9212,10310]}